        96.0,
        262.97,
        187.03,
        274.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p046_s0010",
      "text": "The ESTC ELS is used to estimate the minimum Credit required to achieve the maximum bandwidth",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        286.96,
        539.89,
        298.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p046_s0011",
      "text": "for a given distance between an Nx_Port pair.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        298.96,
        298.28,
        310.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p046_s0012",
      "text": "The class of the SOF of the ESTC Request identifies the class for which Credit is being estimated.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        322.96,
        540.11,
        334.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p046_s0013",
      "text": "The destination Nx_Port shall acknowledge Data frames as specified by its Login parameters.  See",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        334.96,
        539.93,
        346.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
